  "title": "Common Sense",
  "description": "This mod adds crafting recipes for lots of items that don't have crafting recipes, and adds food and items",
  "body": "Welcome to the common sense Mod!\n\nThis mod adds 200+ recipes to blocks/Items that don't have recipes. While also adding Blocks/Items/Tools/Armor to minecraft that makes sense to have Such as, \"Stone Armor\", \"Rotten Leather\" and \"Battle Axes\"\n\n<strong>As of: 10/23/2023 Common sense (Fabric) version is no longer getting updates.</strong><p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>new Wiki!<br><a href=\"https://commonsensemodwiki.weebly.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://the-rtg-gaming-mods.weebly.com/uploads/1/6/7/5/16757746/wiki-button_orig.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"252\" height=\"47\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>\nHere are some images for example\n<p>\n<p><strong> Name Tag</strong></p>\n<img src=\"https://theartggaming.weebly.com/uploads/1/6/7/5/16757746/craft-nametag_orig.png\" alt=\"a 3 by 3 crafting recipe for the nametag: row 1 — empty, string, empty, row 2 — empty, chain ring, string, row 3 — oak sign, empty, empty\" width=\"455\" height=\"215\" />\n<p>\n<p><strong> Bell</strong></p>\n<img src=\"https://theartggaming.weebly.com/uploads/1/6/7/5/16757746/craft-bell-new_orig.png\" alt=\"a 3 by 3 crafting recipe for the bell: row 1 — stone, stick, stone, row 2 — stone, gold ingot, stone, row 3 — stone, gold nugget, stone\" width=\"455\" height=\"215\" />\n<p>\n<p><strong> Crying Obsidian</strong></p>\n<img src=\"https://theartggaming.weebly.com/uploads/1/6/7/5/16757746/craft-crying-obsidia_orig.png\" alt=\"a 3 by 3 crafting recipe for the crying obsidian: row 1 — empty, ghast tear, empty, row 2 — ghast tear, obsidian, ghast tear, row 3 — empty, ghast tear, empty\" width=\"455\" height=\"215\" />\n<p>\n<p><strong> Saddle</strong></p>\n<img src=\"https://theartggaming.weebly.com/uploads/1/6/7/5/16757746/craft-saddle_orig.png\" alt=\"a 3 by 3 crafting recipe for the saddle: row 1 — lead, empty, empty, row 2 — leather, leather, leather, row 3 — leather, empty, tripwire hook\" width=\"455\" height=\"215\" />\n<p>\n\n(made by Mcreator)\n\n<p><strong>wish to join the discord server</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://discord.gg/P3gP4Zm9s6\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/643280/description_7d1286be-0c01-46c5-b971-62cb815cb38b.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"130\" height=\"34\"></a>\n\n<p>----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>",
